"ogimage":"http://s3-media2.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/KgHk06gQ_rffsM2sb4R_6w/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.5",
"reviewcomment":"Oh my gosh. I came here for my last meal in Zurich and man was it a good choice. Thanks to Simon... wooop. We had reservations for the buffet and you can either choose to weigh a first plate or just take the all you can eat for 28CHF. That is an amazing deal for the food that they have! I don&#39;t remember the exact names of the dishes but I&#39;ll do my best. <br><br>The soup was fantastic and was different from any type of soup I&#39;ve had before. It was at first quite sour but then creamy and amazing. Wow, I&#39;d love to have another cup of that. <br>The next several dishes were all different, with wonderful textures, temperatures, and spices. I really enjoyed this ground (beef?) that had an insane amount of flavor and was actually cold. I had seconds. <br>Then there was a chicken curry which was equally delicious. Creamy and bold but not too spicy. The chicken was cooked wonderfully and it was juicy as can be. <br>There was also a fish dish which I didn&#39;t even notice was fish. I thought it was chicken... which I think is usually a good thing with fish. Not too many people like really REALLY fishy tasting fish. But anyway, it was soft and mild and melted in my mouth. <br>They also had a spicy tofu dish. Just the right amount of spice but not enough to overpower the entire meal. And the tofu was tasty too!<br>Last came a nice vegetable dish. Just a bunch of wonderfully marinated vegetables to add a nice variety to the buffet without stuffing everyone over the edge. <br><br>The place was pretty packed during lunch hour, so I&#39;d recommend a reservation. It took us a little time to find the location because it&#39;s cozied into the side streets of downtown Zurich, but you&#39;ll have fun searching because everything is so cute and pretty. I can&#39;t wait to come back here again... it was truly delicious. <br><br>Ich liebe Thai Essen! Und ich liebe Ban Song Thai. Das Essen ist wirchlich toll. Ein Fruend und ich hatten den Buffet und es hat viel viel essen. Alles Essen sind lecker und fantastich. Die Kellner war nett und wir haben ein sehr gut Zeit. Ich mochte Ban Song Thai JETZT!",
